---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Kassie Armbruster, LLC">
  <section class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: February 2025</p>

      <div class="legal-content">
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>Kassie Armbruster, LLC ("we," "our," or "us") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting the personal information you share with us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit our website or use our contact form.</p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>When you use our contact form, we may collect the following information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Full name</li>
          <li>Email address</li>
          <li>Phone number (if provided)</li>
          <li>Service preferences</li>
          <li>Message content</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information you provide to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Respond to your inquiries</li>
          <li>Schedule appointments</li>
          <li>Provide information about our services</li>
          <li>Communicate with you about your care</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Information Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties. Your information is used solely for the purposes described above.</p>

        <h2>Data Security</h2>
        <p>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.</p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Request access to your personal information</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your information</li>
          <li>Opt out of future communications</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>This website does not use tracking cookies or analytics. We may use essential cookies required for the website to function properly.</p>

        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your information, please <a href="/#contact">contact us</a> through our website.</p>

        <div class="legal-note">
          <p><strong>Note:</strong> This Privacy Policy applies to information collected through this website. Healthcare services are subject to separate HIPAA privacy practices, which will be provided to you directly as part of your care.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="/" class="btn-secondary">Back to Home</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: var(--spacing-3xl) 0;
  }

  .legal-page h1 {
    color: var(--primary-dark);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .last-updated {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .legal-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .legal-content h2 {
    color: var(--primary-color);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: var(--spacing-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .legal-content p,
  .legal-content li {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .legal-content ul {
    margin-left: var(--spacing-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
  }

  .legal-content li {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
  }

  .legal-note {
    background-color: var(--background-alt);
    padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-xl);
  }

  .legal-note p {
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>
